---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-background border-t border-foreground/5 py-8 mt-auto">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <p class="text-sm font-black tracking-tighter text-foreground/40 mb-2">
            <span class="text-primary">PO</span><span class="text-secondary">SA</span><span class="text-accent">LA</span><span class="text-foreground">NA</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs text-foreground/30">&copy; {currentYear} - Que la suerte esté de tu lado.</p>
    </div>
</footer>
